@startuml
title L&J Doces - Diagrama de Casos de Uso (MVP)
left to right direction

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FCFCFA
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E8
  BorderColor #8D5A00
  ArrowColor #555555
}

actor "Cliente" as Cliente
actor "Administrador" as Admin
actor "Sistema" as Sistema
actor "IA" as IA

rectangle "L&J Doces - Plataforma" {
  package "1) Jornada do Cliente" {
    usecase "UC01 Consultar\nCatalogo em Tempo Real" as UC01
    usecase "UC02 Autenticar e\nRecuperar Acesso" as UC02
    usecase "UC03 Gerenciar\nPerfil e Favoritos" as UC03
    usecase "UC07 Checkout\ne Pedidos" as UC07
  }

  package "2) Jornada Administrativa" {
    usecase "UC04 Gerenciar\nCatalogo e Categorias" as UC04
    usecase "UC05 Controlar\nEstoque e Alertas" as UC05
    usecase "UC06 Registrar Vendas\ne Penduricalhos" as UC06
    usecase "UC09 Administrar\nBanners e Destaques" as UC09
    usecase "UC10 Consultar\nResumo e Analytics" as UC10
  }

  package "3) Capacidades Transversais" {
    usecase "UC08 Operar Offline\ne Sincronizar" as UC08
    usecase "UC11 Receber Atualizacoes\npor WebSocket" as UC11
    usecase "UC12 Receber Sugestao\nde Producao por IA" as UC12
  }

  package "4) Regras Compartilhadas" {
    usecase "Validar Sessao" as Auth
    usecase "Validar Estoque" as Stock
    usecase "Sincronizar Eventos" as Sync
  }
}

Cliente --> UC01
Cliente --> UC02
Cliente --> UC03
Cliente --> UC07

Admin --> UC04
Admin --> UC05
Admin --> UC06
Admin --> UC09
Admin --> UC10
Admin --> UC12

Sistema --> UC08
Sistema --> UC11
IA --> UC12

' Links ocultos para travar posicionamento e reduzir sobreposição visual
UC01 -[hidden]-> UC04
UC04 -[hidden]-> UC08
UC08 -[hidden]-> Auth
Auth -[hidden]-> Stock
Stock -[hidden]-> Sync

UC03 .> Auth : <<include>>
UC04 .> Auth : <<include>>
UC07 .> Auth : <<include>>
UC09 .> Auth : <<include>>
UC10 .> Auth : <<include>>

UC07 .> Stock : <<include>>
UC05 .> Stock : <<include>>

UC08 .> Sync : <<include>>
UC11 .> Sync : <<include>>
UC10 .> UC12 : <<extend>>

note bottom
Referencias principais: UC01-UC12 em docs/01-visao/mvp.md
e regras RN-01 a RN-16 em docs/02-requisitos/RN.md.
end note

note right of Auth
Para reduzir poluicao visual,
nem todos os includes repetidos
foram desenhados.
As regras continuam valendo
para os demais casos aplicaveis.
end note

@enduml
